    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>chestnut</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong>, then peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated mushrooms</strong>, <strong>grated garlic</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter </strong>to the dish</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
