      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, <strong>dried oregano </strong>and 650ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[845ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1.1L]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat, season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong>, then cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for an initial 30 min – this is your <strong>mushroom ragù</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
