      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After 30 min, remove the <strong>mushroom ragù</strong> from the oven and give it a good stir</p><p>Break your <strong>spaghetti</strong> in half and add it to the dish, giving everything a good mix up to separate the strands</p><p>Return the dish to the oven and cook, covered, for a final 25 min or until the spaghetti is tender – this is your<strong> all-in-one mushroom ragù spaghetti</strong></p>",
