      "instruction": "<p>To serve, give the <strong>all-in-one mushroom ragù spaghetti</strong> a good mix up with a fork to separate the strands of pasta and sprinkle your <strong>grated</strong> <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> all over</p><p>Serve the <strong>caprese salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Dig in!</p>",
